Package org.openjena.atlas.data

Interface Summary
DataBag<T> A collection of Tuples.
SerializationFactory<E>  
ThresholdPolicy<E>  
 

Class Summary
AbstractDataBag<E> Abstract implementation of DataBag.
BagFactory Factory for constructing different types of DataBag instances.
DefaultDataBag<E> This data bag will gather items in memory until a size threshold is passed, at which point it will write out all of the items to disk using the supplied serializer.
DistinctDataBag<E> This data bag will gather distinct items in memory until a size threshold is passed, at which point it will write out all of the items to disk using the supplied serializer.
SortedDataBag<E> This data bag will gather items in memory until a size threshold is passed, at which point it will write out all of the items to disk using the supplied serializer.
ThresholdPolicyCount<T> A threshold policy based on the number of tuples added.
ThresholdPolicyMemory<T> A threshold policy based on the estimated memory size of the tuples added.
ThresholdPolicyNever<T> A threshold policy that is never exceeded.
